data.meta_description: Mahesh Bhupathi - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides biographical information about Indian tennis player Mahesh Bhupathi. It details his career accomplishments as a doubles player, including winning 52 doubles titles and reaching number 1 in the world rankings. It notes that he won 3 Grand Slam doubles titles with Leander Paes in 1999 and had a successful mixed doubles career as well, achieving a career Grand Slam in that event. The document provides an overview of Bhupathi's playing career from 1995-2013 and his accomplishments with various partners over the years.
